<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Giriş Yap | Güllüce İletişim</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr,0.9fr] items-start">
      <section class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-indigo-500 to-cyan-400 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_20%,_white,_transparent_35%)]"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
          <p class="section-label text-white/80">Giriş</p>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight">
            Hoş geldin! Sipariş ve sepet bilgilerine erişmek için giriş yap.
          </h1>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/90">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>✅</span><span>Sepetini cihazlar arasında senkronize et.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>✅</span><span>Yeni gelen ürünleri hızlıca kaydet.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>✅</span><span>Adres ve sipariş geçmişine tek panelden eriş.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card glass">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs text-indigo-500 font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Giriş Yap</p>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Hesabına devam et</h2>
          </div>
          <a href="/auth/register" class="text-xs text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Hesabın yok mu?</a>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-red-600 bg-red-50 border border-red-100 rounded-lg px-3 py-2">
            <%= error %>
          </p>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/auth/login" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-1">E-posta</label>
            <input
              id="email"
              name="email"
              type="email"
              required
              value="<%= form?.email || '' %>"
              class="input"
              placeholder="mail@ornek.com"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="password" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-1">Şifre</label>
            <input
              id="password"
              name="password"
              type="password"
              required
              class="input"
              placeholder="Şifreniz"
            />
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn-primary w-full justify-center">
            Giriş Yap
          </button>
        </form>

        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-4">
          Şifreni unuttuysan bizimle iletişime geçebilirsin. Güvenlik için tek cihazdan giriş açık kalır.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
